      "writtenOn": "2017-02-02T15:43:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not convinced this assert is guaranteed to be true.\n\nCan the frame be offset by an odd amount? If so, and it is less than fSubset, then (e.g.) minXOffset will be odd. Subtract that odd number from the even fSubset, and you\u0027ll end up with an odd number.\n\n(It would be good to have a test to verify this.)",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 276,
        "startChar": 17,
